casebody.data:
Marion WILSON, Jr., petitioner,
v.
Benjamin FORD, Warden. No. 18-9746 (18A1346). Supreme Court of the United States June 20, 2019.

*2739Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice THOMAS and by him referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Georgia denied.
